data.description: A MAJOR renovation has made this beautiful central Florida bungalow come to life! NEW floors! NEW frame, walls and paint! NEW roof! NEW AC! NEW electrical and plumping! NEW bathrooms, and NEW Kitchen! Most of the brand new windows are impact resistant for hurricane winds! Horses and other livestock are welcome on the 1.91 acres, zoned ASC1. Plenty of shade from large oak trees as well as a nice section of cleared land to do with what you please! Dead end street with large lots and plenty of privacy.  This house is worth a look, 1218 sq ft has never felt so big!
